name: Unikat
description:
Create your very own generative art with the design tool you already love.


  • Test, tweak and ship generative art without coding skills
  • Perfect to create NFT collections
  • 100% free — now and forever
  • Powerful rarity feature — just stick to Unikat’s layer name convention
  • Straight-forward and simple UI
  • Step-by-step help built-in
